	(text_box "IC Notes: \n\nThe TPA3110D2 is a 15-W (per channel) efficient, Class-D audio power amplifier for driving bridged-tied stereo speakers.\n\nVBATT Voltage Range: 8 V to 26 V\n90% Efficient Class-D Amp Eliminates Need for Heat Sinks\nFilter-Free Operation\nAdjustable Power Limiter\nSpeaker DC Current Protection\nRobust Pin-to-Pin Short Circuit Protection and Thermal Protection\nExcellent THD+N / Pop-Free Performance\nFour Selectable, Fixed Gain Settings\nDifferential Inputs\nDigital Inputs compatible with TTL logic"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 190.5 30.48 0)
		(size 72.39 40.64)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
