	(text_box "XSMT pin is used for soft mute and unplanned shutdown. MCU can set DAC_MUTE high to mute DAC. In addition, if 5V supply goes down DAC will begin soft mute ramp. 5V rail must not exceed 5.5V to prevent damage to the DAC!"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 63.5 228.6 0)
